  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13064813/walkers-rucksack.jpg" alt="Walkers rucksack" rel="858,410" /></div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>Whether hiking in the mountains or strolling by the lakes, a good quality rucksack is essential and we’re offering all our guests booking their Summer 2016 holiday <strong>a <span style="color: red;">FREE</span> walkers’ rucksack per couple,</strong> while stocks last!</strong></p>
<p>It is also possible to purchase further rucksacks, if stocks allow, and only for existing guests. We will offer these for £25, a discount of £14 of their full price of £39. Please order your rucksack at time of booking.</p>
<p>It has 22 litres capacity and a wealth of useful features including padded adjustable shoulder, a breathable mesh back-panel, mesh side-pockets for your water bottle and even an attachment point for your walking poles. And its dimensions are well within our airlines’ hand baggage regulations.</p>
<p>Rucksacks will be sent out by our appointed independent distributor (Colourgraphics). <strong>To claim your free rucksack</strong>, simply email <a href="mailto:rucksack@colourgraphic-arts.co.uk">rucksack@colourgraphic-arts.co.uk</a> (or ask your travel agent to email for you), providing your <strong>booking reference, lead name and required postal delivery address</strong>.</p>
<p>If you do not have email access, please call John Scardarella on 01428 772 230.</p>
<p>To purchase an additional rucksack, please call our hotline on 01483 791122. Optional rucksacks at £25 will be offered at time of booking. If you have booked through a travel agent, please contact them directly to make payment and they will arrange rucksack delivery on your behalf.</p>
<p>See <a href="/{localLink:66d6dfd2-b127-48e8-b6d8-228d6e59ea65}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a> for further details. <strong>Free Rucksack Offer:</strong> All name &amp; address information supplied to the distributor in conjunction with this promotion will be destroyed after despatch and will not be used for any future marketing activity by them or by Inghams. Guests’ addresses supplied to them by travel agents will not be passed to Inghams at any time.</p>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
